This paper discusses a new DDoS defense mechanism for ISPs, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also presents a multi-layered defense architecture, which involves system design and implementation (cs.SY), distributed systems (cs.DC), and software engineering (cs.SE).
